<plist version="1.0">
    <!-- See https://aka.ms/maui-publish-app-store#add-entitlements for more information about adding entitlements.
         App Sandbox is intentionally NOT enabled so dev (`make run`) shares the same
         ~/Library data root as the signed release (which also ships unsandboxed).
         With the sandbox on, MAUI's FileSystem.AppDataDirectory resolved to
         ~/Library/Containers/<bundle-id>/Data/Library and dev couldn't see the
         release's certificates.json / activity.json / certificates/ folder. -->
